                            <p>It's not necessarily just a child. But that's what we're focused on, because that's our journey. We became aware of Alan onto some friends, a friend that I've had for over 30 years or more. And her son had been addicted to heroin. And so she was involved in Alainan, and she had remarried a man that was in recovery in AA.</p>

