                            <p>But I felt like, you know, you get a strain and you pull it. I felt like I got that. That's it. And I was terrified because this was not a good story. But I also felt like there was some ground in my feet finally, you know.</p>

                            <p>OK, now we can explore this a little bit more. So we began attending Alan on. But we began attending Alan on. And he's progressing quickly in his disease. Not long after his expelli had his first car accident.</p>

